WEBVTT

00:00.344 --> 00:01.702
My name
is Michael Westen.

00:01.771 --> 00:04.285
I used to be
a spy until...

00:04.286 --> 00:05.354
We got a burn notice on you.

00:05.421 --> 00:07.282
You're blacklisted.

00:07.350 --> 00:09.617
When you're burned,
you've got nothing.

00:09.684 --> 00:11.915
No cash, no credit,
no job history.

00:11.982 --> 00:14.257
You're stuck in whatever city
they decide to dump you in.

00:14.325 --> 00:16.689
- Where am I?
- Miami.

00:16.757 --> 00:19.026
You do whatever work
comes your way.

00:19.094 --> 00:21.197
You rely on anyone
who's still talking to you...

00:22.733 --> 00:23.666
A trigger-happy girlfriend...

00:23.733 --> 00:25.100
Should we shoot them?

00:25.168 --> 00:27.002
An old friend who used
to inform on you to the FBI...

00:27.069 --> 00:28.336
You know spies--

00:28.404 --> 00:29.706
bunch of bitchy little girls.

00:29.773 --> 00:31.109
Family too...

00:31.177 --> 00:32.009
Hey, is that your mom again?

00:32.077 --> 00:33.177
If you're desperate.

00:33.245 --> 00:34.525
Someone needs your help,
Michael.

00:34.547 --> 00:37.217
And a down-and-out spy
you met along the way.

00:37.285 --> 00:38.852
That's how we do it, people.

00:38.920 --> 00:41.592
Bottom line,
as long as you're burned,

00:41.660 --> 00:43.495
you're not going anywhere.

00:45.765 --> 00:47.199
This is the only offer
you will get.

00:47.266 --> 00:48.969
We're going after the leader
of a terrorist network

00:49.037 --> 00:50.905
based in
the Dominican Republic.

00:50.973 --> 00:52.640
- Burke.
- I got a job coming up.

00:52.707 --> 00:56.312
I was hoping you might
be right for it.

00:56.379 --> 00:57.947
I'll be in touch,
but I want you to keep

00:58.015 --> 00:59.382
a low profile
until I get back.

00:59.450 --> 01:00.750
And be ready.

01:00.818 --> 01:04.221
Michael Westen was
still working for the CIA.

01:04.289 --> 01:06.390
You are going to put me
in touch with him.

01:06.457 --> 01:10.761
Fi, it's time to be brave,
little angel.

